{"tid":1734464,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"香港-東方之珠？國際大都會？","createTime":"2019-11-18T10:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T14:13:02.000Z","uid":225568,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"054dbe6037ddf05bb103543afcc3ac118329dfb8","tid":1734464,"uid":225568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"我呸！<br />\n班國際吸血蟲淨係識來香港吸血！<br />\n用香港人的血、汗、智土地來搵錢！<br />\n到香港人有事的時候，有無國際企業出聲？<br />\n有無國際企業幫手？有無國際企業帶頭罷工？<br />\n無呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中環金鐘幾靚有咩用？<br />\n租金幾高只系特顯自己有幾巴閉<br />\n成班國際吸血蟲根本只系當香港係搵錢機械！<br />\n呢兩日的事令我我敢肯定，全部國際企業系香港有事，或者香港唔掂/淪陷的時候，只會撤資自保！根本唔撚會幫我地！<br />\n香港的繁榮穩定只不過係用金錢堆砌出來的糖衣外殼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真系好嬲，現代文明，人權，人道，全部都不及搵錢重要！你班建立係文明社會的國際吸血蟲！<br />\n共產黨如果他朝有日控制曬你地，記得你地有份比錢比技術養肥佢呀！！！<br />\n比翻d手足我地呀！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/